    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const coreContext = $items(\"Get Core Brand Context\")[0].json.Content;\n\nconst outputRules = $items(\"Get Core Output Rules\")[0].json.Content;\n\nconst platformPrompt = $items(\"Get Etsy Prompt\")[0].json.Content;\n\nconst productPrompt = $items(\"Get Product Prompt\")[0].json.Content;\n\nconst brand = $items(\"Get Brand Profile\")[0].json;\n\nconst finalPrompt = `\n${coreContext}\n\n${outputRules}\n\n${platformPrompt}\n\n${productPrompt}\n\nBrand: ${brand.Brand}\nProduct: ${brand.Product}\nNiche: ${brand.Niche}\nAudience: ${brand.Audience}\nStyle: ${brand.Style}\nColors: ${brand.Colors}\nTone: ${brand.Tone}\nLanguage: ${brand.Language}\nMarket: ${brand.Market}\nGoal: ${brand.Goal}\n\nGenerate a high-converting Etsy listing.\n\nReturn ONLY valid JSON using this structure:\n\n{\n  \"etsy_title\":\"\",\n  \"short_description\":\"\",\n  \"full_description\":\"\",\n  \"seo_keywords\":[],\n  \"tags\":[],\n  \"target_audience\":\"\",\n  \"benefits\":[],\n  \"mockup_ideas\":[],\n  \"faq\":[],\n  \"cta\":\"\"\n}\n`;\nreturn [\n  {\n    json: {\n      prompt: finalPrompt\n    },\n    pairedItem: { item: 0 }\n  }\n];"
      },
